Fast.and.Furious.2006.mkv.title: The Fast and the Furious: Tokyo Drift

Fight.Club.1999.mkv.title: Fight Club

Fist.of.fury.mkv.title: Fist of Fury

Enter.the.dragon.mkv.title: Enter the Dragon

fist_fight.mp4.title: Fist Fight

Fullmetal.Alchemist.2017.mkv.title: 鋼の錬金術師
Fullmetal.Alchemist.2017.mkv.plot: Two alchemist brothers go on a quest for the Philosopher's Stone after an attempt to revive their dead mother goes horribly wrong.

Game.Night.2018.mp4.title: Game Night

The friends soon find themselves in over their heads as each twist leads to another unexpected turn over the course of one chaotic night.

Game.of.death.II.mkv.title: Si wang ta

Drone.2017.mkv.title: Drone

Game.of.death.mkv.title: Game of Death

Gringo.2018.mkv.title: Gringo

Harry.Potter.and.the.Deathly.Hallows.Par.title: Harry Potter and the Deathly Hallows: Part 2

Harry.Potter.and.the.Prisoner.of.Azkaban.title: Harry Potter and the Prisoner of Azkaban

Hellboy.2019.mkv.title: Hellboy

High.Life.2018.mkv.title: High Life

Hobbs.and.Shaw.2019.mkv.title: Fast & Furious Presents: Hobbs & Shaw

Hustlers.2019..mkv.title: Hustlers

Idiocracy.2006.mp4.title: Idiocracy

But when they arrive, they find a civilization so dumbed-down that they're the smartest people around.

INCEPTION.mp4.title: Inception
INCEPTION.mp4.plot: Cobb, a skilled thief who commits corporate espionage by infiltrating the subconscious of his targets is offered a chance to regain his old life as payment for a task considered to be impossible: "inception", the implantation of another person's idea into a target's subconscious.

Incident.in.a.Ghost.Land.2018.mkv.title: Ghostland
Incident.in.a.Ghost.Land.2018.mkv.plot: A mother of two inherits a home from her aunt. Sixteen years later the daughters reunite at the house, and that is when things get strange . . .

Iron Man 1.avi.title: Iron Man
Iron Man 1.avi.plot: After being held captive in an Afghan cave, billionaire engineer Tony Stark creates a unique weaponized suit of armor to fight evil.

Jojo.Rabbit.2019.mkv.title: Jojo Rabbit

Aided only by his idiotic imaginary friend, Adolf Hitler, Jojo must confront his blind nationalism.

Incontrol.2017.mp4.title: Incontrol

Interstellar.2014.mkv.title: Interstellar
Interstellar.2014.mkv.plot: The adventures of a group of explorers who make use of a newly discovered wormhole to surpass the limitations on human space travel and conquer the vast distances involved in an interstellar voyage.

Iron Man 3.mp4.title: Iron Man 3
Iron Man 3.mp4.plot: When Tony Stark's world is torn apart by a formidable terrorist called the Mandarin, he starts an odyssey of rebuilding and retribution.

Iron.Man.2.2010.mp4.title: Iron Man 2
Iron.Man.2.2010.mp4.plot: With the world now aware of his dual life as the armored superhero Iron Man, billionaire inventor Tony Stark faces pressure from the government, the press and the public to share his technology with the military. Unwilling to let go of his invention, Stark, with Pepper Potts and James 'Rhodey' Rhodes at his side, must forge new alliances – and confront powerful enemies.

Jeepers.Creepers.III.2017.mkv.title: Jeepers Creepers 3
Jeepers.Creepers.III.2017.mkv.plot: Taking place on the last day of the Creeper’s twenty-three-day feeding frenzy, as the skeptical Sergeant Tubbs teams up with a task force hellbent on destroying the Creeper for good. The Creeper fights back in gory glory as its enemies grow closer than ever before to learning the secret of its dark origins.

John Carter (2012).mkv.title: John Carter

It's a world on the brink of collapse, and Carter rediscovers his humanity when he realizes the survival of Barsoom and its people rests in his hands.

Johnny.English.Strikes.Again.2018.mp4.title: Johnny English Strikes Again

For this mission to succeed, he’ll need all of his skills - what few he has - as the man with yesterday’s analogue methods faces off against tomorrow’s digital technology.

John Tucker Must Die.avi.title: John Tucker Must Die
John Tucker Must Die.avi.plot: After discovering they are all dating the same same guy, three popular students from different cliques band together for revenge, so they enlist the help of a new gal in town and conspire to break the jerk's heart, while destroying his reputation.

Joker.2019.mkv.title: Joker

Iron.Sky.2.2019.mkv.title: Iron Sky

Isle.of.Dogs.2018.mkv.title: Isle of Dogs

Jexi.2019.mkv.title: Jexi

Jurassic.Park.III.2001.1080p.mp4.title: Jurassic Park III

Jurassic.World.Fallen.Kingdom.2018.mkv.title: Jurassic World: Fallen Kingdom

Kill.Bill.Volume.1.2003.720p.mp4.title: Kill Bill: Vol. 1
Kill.Bill.Volume.1.2003.720p.mp4.plot: An assassin is shot by her ruthless employer, Bill, and other members of their assassination circle – but she lives to plot her vengeance.

Kill.Bill.Volume.2.2004.mp4.title: Kill Bill: Vol. 2
Kill.Bill.Volume.2.2004.mp4.plot: The Bride unwaveringly continues on her roaring rampage of revenge against the band of assassins who had tried to kill her and her unborn child. She visits each of her former associates one-by-one, checking off the victims on her Death List Five until there's nothing left to do … but kill Bill.

Lion.King.2019.mkv.title: The Lion King
Lion.King.2019.mkv.plot: Simba idolizes his father, King Mufasa, and takes to heart his own royal destiny. But not everyone in the kingdom celebrates the new cub's arrival. Scar, Mufasa's brother—and former heir to the throne—has plans of his own. The battle for Pride Rock is ravaged with betrayal, tragedy and drama, ultimately resulting in Simba's exile. With help from a curious pair of newfound friends, Simba will have to figure out how to grow up and take back what is rightfully his.

Law Abiding Citizen (2009).mkv.title: Law Abiding Citizen
Law Abiding Citizen (2009).mkv.plot: A frustrated man decides to take justice into his own hands after a plea bargain sets one of his family's killers free. He targets not only the killer but also the district attorney and others involved in the deal.

Looking.Glass.2018.mkv.title: Looking Glass

In a twisted game of cat and mouse, Ray must race to save his wife and himself from a gruesome secret connected to the motel and the strange people who visit there.

Jurassic.Park.1993.1080p.mp4.title: Jurassic Park

Before opening day, he invites a team of experts and his two eager grandchildren to experience the park and help calm anxious investors. However, the park is anything but amusing as the security systems go off-line and the dinosaurs escape.

Kidnapping.Mr..Heineken.mp4.title: Kidnapping Mr. Heineken

Mandy.2018.mkv.title: Mandy

Murderous consequences unravel in the dead of night, as their lives intertwine at the hands of a mysterious criminal mastermind who is hell-bent on revenge.

Terminator.Genisys.2015.1080p.mkv.title: Terminator Genisys
Terminator.Genisys.2015.1080p.mkv.plot: The year is 2029. John Connor, leader of the resistance continues the war against the machines. At the Los Angeles offensive, John's fears of the unknown future begin to emerge when TECOM spies reveal a new plot by SkyNet that will attack him from both fronts; past and future, and will ultimately change warfare forever.

The Avengers 2012.mp4.title: The Avengers
The Avengers 2012.mp4.plot: When an unexpected enemy emerges and threatens global safety and security, Nick Fury, director of the international peacekeeping agency known as S.H.I.E.L.D., finds himself in need of a team to pull the world back from the brink of disaster. Spanning the globe, a daring recruitment effort begins!

The Abyss [1989].mkv.title: The Abyss
The Abyss [1989].mkv.plot: A civilian oil rig crew is recruited to conduct a search and rescue effort when a nuclear submarine mysteriously sinks. One diver soon finds himself on a spectacular odyssey 25,000 feet below the ocean's surface where he confronts a mysterious force that has the power to change the world or destroy it.

The Dark Tower 2017.mp4.title: The Dark Tower
The Dark Tower 2017.mp4.plot: The last Gunslinger, Roland Deschain, has been locked in an eternal battle with Walter O’Dim, also known as the Man in Black, determined to prevent him from toppling the Dark Tower, which holds the universe together. With the fate of the worlds at stake, good and evil will collide in the ultimate battle as only Roland can defend the Tower from the Man in Black.

The Belko Experiment.mkv.title: The Belko Experiment
The Belko Experiment.mkv.plot: A group of eighty American workers are locked in their office and ordered by an unknown voice to participate in a twisted game.

Terminator.Salvation.2009.1080p.mkv.title: Terminator Salvation
Terminator.Salvation.2009.1080p.mkv.plot: All grown up in post-apocalyptic 2018, John Connor must lead the resistance of humans against the increasingly dominating militaristic robots. But when Marcus Wright appears, his existence confuses the mission as Connor tries to determine whether Wright has come from the future or the past -- and whether he's friend or foe.

The Dark Knight Rises (2012).mp4.title: The Dark Knight Rises
The Dark Knight Rises (2012).mp4.plot: Following the death of District Attorney Harvey Dent, Batman assumes responsibility for Dent's crimes to protect the late attorney's reputation and is subsequently hunted by the Gotham City Police Department. Eight years later, Batman encounters the mysterious Selina Kyle and the villainous Bane, a new terrorist leader who overwhelms Gotham's finest. The Dark Knight resurfaces to protect a city that has branded him an enemy.

The Fifth Element.1997.mkv.title: The Fifth Element
The Fifth Element.1997.mkv.plot: In 2257, a taxi driver is unintentionally given the task of saving a young girl who is part of the key that will ensure the survival of humanity.

The Lord of the Rings 2 (2002).mkv.title: The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers
The Lord of the Rings 2 (2002).mkv.plot: Frodo and Sam are trekking to Mordor to destroy the One Ring of Power while Gimli, Legolas and Aragorn search for the orc-captured Merry and Pippin. All along, nefarious wizard Saruman awaits the Fellowship members at the Orthanc Tower in Isengard.

The Lord of the Rings 1 (2001).mkv.title: The Lord of the Rings: The Fellowship of the Ring
The Lord of the Rings 1 (2001).mkv.plot: Young hobbit Frodo Baggins, after inheriting a mysterious ring from his uncle Bilbo, must leave his home in order to keep it from falling into the hands of its evil creator. Along the way, a fellowship is formed to protect the ringbearer and make sure that the ring arrives at its final destination: Mt. Doom, the only place where it can be destroyed.

The Lord of the Rings 3 (2003).mkv.title: The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King
The Lord of the Rings 3 (2003).mkv.plot: Aragorn is revealed as the heir to the ancient kings as he, Gandalf and the other members of the broken fellowship struggle to save Gondor from Sauron's forces. Meanwhile, Frodo and Sam take the ring closer to the heart of Mordor, the dark lord's realm.

The Losers (2010).avi.title: The Losers
The Losers (2010).avi.plot: A tale of double cross and revenge, centered upon the members of an elite U.S. Special Forces unit sent into the Bolivian jungle on a search and destroy mission. The team-Clay, Jensen, Roque, Pooch and Cougar -find themselves the target of a lethal betrayal instigated from inside by a powerful enemy known only as Max. Presumed dead, the group makes plans to even the score when they're joined by the mysterious Aisha, a beautiful operative with her own agenda. Working together, they must remain deep undercover while tracking the heavily-guarded Max, a ruthless man bent on embroiling the world in a new high-tech global war.

The Man from UNCLE.mp4.title: The Man from U.N.C.L.E.
The Man from UNCLE.mp4.plot: At the height of the Cold War, a mysterious criminal organization plans to use nuclear weapons and technology to upset the fragile balance of power between the United States and Soviet Union. CIA agent Napoleon Solo and KGB agent Illya Kuryakin are forced to put aside their hostilities and work together to stop the evildoers in their tracks. The duo's only lead is the daughter of a missing German scientist, whom they must find soon to prevent a global catastrophe.

The Package (2018).mp4.title: The Package
The Package (2018).mp4.plot: When a group of teenagers goes on a spring break camping trip, an unfortunate accident sets off a race to save their friend’s most prized possession.

The Mummy 1999.mp4.title: The Mummy
The Mummy 1999.mp4.plot: Dashing legionnaire Rick O'Connell stumbles upon the hidden ruins of Hamunaptra while in the midst of a battle to claim the area in 1920s Egypt. It has been over three thousand years since former High Priest Imhotep suffered a fate worse than death as a punishment for a forbidden love—along with a curse that guarantees eternal doom upon the world if he is ever awoken.

The Shawshank Redemption.mkv.title: The Shawshank Redemption
The Shawshank Redemption.mkv.plot: Framed in the 1940s for the double murder of his wife and her lover, upstanding banker Andy Dufresne begins a new life at the Shawshank prison, where he puts his accounting skills to work for an amoral warden. During his long stretch in prison, Dufresne comes to be admired by the other inmates -- including an older prisoner named Red -- for his integrity and unquenchable sense of hope.

The Terminator 1984.mp4.title: The Terminator
The Terminator 1984.mp4.plot: In the post-apocalyptic future, reigning tyrannical supercomputers teleport a cyborg assassin known as the "Terminator" back to 1984 to kill Sarah Connor, whose unborn son is destined to lead insurgents against 21st century mechanical hegemony. Meanwhile, the human-resistance movement dispatches a lone warrior to safeguard Sarah. Can he stop the virtually indestructible killing machine?

The Simpsons Movie.mkv.title: The Simpsons Movie
The Simpsons Movie.mkv.plot: After Homer accidentally pollutes the town's water supply, Springfield is encased in a gigantic dome by the EPA and the Simpsons are declared fugitives.

The Thing (2011).mkv.title: The Thing
The Thing (2011).mkv.plot: Members of an American scientific research outpost in Antarctica find themselves battling a parasitic alien organism capable of perfectly imitating its victims. They soon discover that this task will be harder than they thought, as they don't know which members of the team have already been assimilated and their paranoia threatens to tear them apart.

The.Accountant.2016.mp4.title: The Accountant
The.Accountant.2016.mp4.plot: As a math savant uncooks the books for a new client, the Treasury Department closes in on his activities and the body count starts to rise.

The Godfather.1972.mkv.title: The Godfather
The Godfather.1972.mkv.plot: Spanning the years 1945 to 1955, a chronicle of the fictional Italian-American Corleone crime family. When organized crime family patriarch, Vito Corleone barely survives an attempt on his life, his youngest son, Michael steps in to take care of the would-be killers, launching a campaign of bloody revenge.

The.Animatrix.2003.mp4.title: The Animatrix
The.Animatrix.2003.mp4.plot: Straight from the creators of the groundbreaking Matrix trilogy, this collection of short animated films from the world's leading anime directors fuses computer graphics and Japanese anime to provide the background of the Matrix universe and the conflict between man and machines. The shorts include Final Flight of the Osiris, The Second Renaissance, Kid's Story, Program, World Record, Beyond, A Detective Story and Matriculated.

The.Art.of.Self.Defense.2019.mkv.title: The Art of Self-Defense
The.Art.of.Self.Defense.2019.mkv.plot: Casey is attacked at random on the street and enlists in a local dojo led by a charismatic and mysterious Sensei in an effort to learn how to defend himself. What he uncovers is a sinister world of fraternity, violence and hypermasculinity and a woman fighting for her place in it.

The.Beach.Bum.2019.mkv.title: The Beach Bum
The.Beach.Bum.2019.mkv.plot: An irreverent comedy about the misadventures of Moondog, a rebellious stoner and lovable rogue who lives large.

The.Beyond.2017.mkv.title: The Beyond
The.Beyond.2017.mkv.plot: Set in 2019, The Beyond chronicles the groundbreaking mission which sent astronauts - modified with advanced robotics, through a newly discovered wormhole known as the Void. When the mission returns unexpectedly, the space agency races to discover what the astronauts encountered on their first of its kind interstellar space journey.

The.curse.of.the.dragon.mkv.title: The Curse of the Dragon
The.curse.of.the.dragon.mkv.plot: A 1993 documentary film about Bruce Lee. The film includes interviews from some of his fellow students and opponents who worked alongside him in his movies.

The.Book.of.Life.2014.1080p.mp4.title: The Book of Life
The.Book.of.Life.2014.1080p.mp4.plot: The journey of Manolo, a young man who is torn between fulfilling the expectations of his family and following his heart. Before choosing which path to follow, he embarks on an incredible adventure that spans three fantastical worlds where he must face his greatest fears.

The.Domestics.2018.mp4.title: The Domestics
The.Domestics.2018.mp4.plot: A young husband and wife must fight to return home in a post-apocalyptic mid-western landscape ravaged by gangs.

The.Debt.Collector.2018.mkv.title: The Debt Collector
The.Debt.Collector.2018.mkv.plot: A classically-trained martial artist goes to work as a debt collector for the mob. The job seems easy enough, until one “client” pulls him into a situation deeper than could ever be expected.

The.Exorcist.1973.mp4.title: The Exorcist
The.Exorcist.1973.mp4.plot: 12-year-old Regan MacNeil begins to adapt an explicit new personality as strange events befall the local area of Georgetown. Her mother becomes torn between science and superstition in a desperate bid to save her daughter, and ultimately turns to her last hope: Father Damien Karras, a troubled priest who is struggling with his own faith.

The.Equalizer.2.2018.mp4.title: The Equalizer
The.Equalizer.2.2018.mp4.plot: McCall believes he has put his mysterious past behind him and dedicated himself to beginning a new, quiet life. But when he meets Teri, a young girl under the control of ultra-violent Russian gangsters, he can’t stand idly by – he has to help her. Armed with hidden skills that allow him to serve vengeance against anyone who would brutalize the helpless, McCall comes out of his self-imposed retirement and finds his desire for justice reawakened. If someone has a problem, if the odds are stacked against them, if they have nowhere else to turn, McCall will help. He is The Equalizer.

The.Expendables.2010.mkv.title: The Expendables
The.Expendables.2010.mkv.plot: Barney Ross leads a band of highly skilled mercenaries including knife enthusiast Lee Christmas, a martial arts expert, heavy weapons specialist, demolitionist, and a loose-cannon sniper. When the group is commissioned by the mysterious Mr. Church to assassinate the dictator of a small South American island, Barney and Lee visit the remote locale to scout out their opposition and discover the true nature of the conflict engulfing the city.

The.Foreigner.2017.mp4.title: The Foreigner
The.Foreigner.2017.mp4.plot: Quan is a humble London businessman whose long-buried past erupts in a revenge-fueled vendetta when the only person left for him to love – his teenage daughter – dies in a senseless act of politically-motivated terrorism. His relentless search to find the terrorists leads to a cat-and-mouse conflict with a British government official whose own past may hold the clues to the identities of the elusive killers.

The.Expendables.2.2012.mkv.title: The Expendables 2
The.Expendables.2.2012.mkv.plot: Mr. Church reunites the Expendables for what should be an easy paycheck, but when one of their men is murdered on the job, their quest for revenge puts them deep in enemy territory and up against an unexpected threat.

The.Gateway.2018.mkv.title: The Gateway
The.Gateway.2018.mkv.plot: Danni moves into a New York apartment and starts sprucing the place up. She doesn’t know the previous tenant committed suicide in very strange circumstances. Nor does she know there’s a mysterious portal to another dimension in the bathroom that’s hungry for….  shower curtains!  But where does this unusual gateway hidden behind the white tiling lead? That’s what Danni and her ‘Whale Saver’ chugger workmate Tim decide to find out. It’s an investigation into a unique phenomenon full of surprise and unimaginable horror as they both enter The Yonder in a stunningly directed, creatively devised and quirky oddball gem.
